listitem.para:
                    
                        Example 2 - Program listing. 
                      
                    It is a verbatim environment for program source or source fragment listings. whitespace and linebreaks within this element are significant.
                    
                    
                        Java program listing
                        
                            public class HelloWorld 
                            {
                                public static void main(String args[]) 
                                {
                                    System.out.println("Hello World!");
                                }
                            }
                        
                    

                    
                    
                        xml code listing
                        
                            <xs:attribute name="src" type="xs:anyURI" />
